text: Dompierre (Dictionnaire-Dikchenéro: Français-Patois/Patê-Franché. Société cantonale des patoisans fribourgeois. Fribourg: 2013. p. 148) was a municipality of the district of Broye, in the canton of Fribourg, in Switzerland. On 1 January 2016, the former municipalities of Domdidier, Dompierre, Léchelles and Russy merged to form the new municipality of Belmont- Broye.Nomenklaturen – Amtliches Gemeindeverzeichnis der Schweiz accessed 3 February 2016 == References == == Other websites == * Official website Category:Former municipalities of Fribourg
